{
  "texts": [
    "On search trials, observers perform the an additional-singleton task.",
    "On probe trials, a letter-probe display appears briefly and is followed by a mask.",
    "In this display, a letter is superimposed on each search stimulus, or sometimes on a subset of these stimuli.",
    "Participants are required to report the letters they saw.",
    "The critical measure is the percentage of correctly reported letters, which serves as an index of attentional priority."
  ]
}